{"tid":812841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【馬雲退下】阿里巴巴：明年9月10日馬雲不再擔任董事局主席","createTime":"2018-09-10T03:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T03:26:06.000Z","uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a94bdd5a5baf17f34b3d48a4ac9cdc10321799cc","tid":812841,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T03:24:20.000Z","msg":"　　《經濟通通訊社10日專訊》阿里巴巴集團宣布，2019年9月10日，馬雲將不再擔任董事局主席，CEO張勇接任。明年9月10日後，馬雲將繼續擔任阿里巴巴集團董事會成員，直到2020年阿里巴巴年度股東大會。馬雲除了繼續擔任阿里巴巴合夥人和為合夥人組織機制做努力和貢獻外，將回歸教育。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2157348/%E3%80%90%E9%A6%AC%E9%9B%B2%E9%80%80%E4%B8%8B%E3%80%91%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B49%E6%9C%8810%E6%97%A5%E9%A6%AC%E9%9B%B2%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%93%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD?mtc=30024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2157348%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%259B%25B2%25E9%2580%2580%25E4%25B8%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%2598%25BF%25E9%2587%258C%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25B7%25B4%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B49%25E6%259C%258810%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%259B%25B2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2593%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%2591%25A3%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%25B1%2580%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%3Fmtc%3D30024&d=0AT3V79WG1rIWdgUzk9SNv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=27e7c73f\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2157348/%E3%80%90%E9%A6%AC%E9%9B%B2%E9%80%80%E4%B8%8B%E3%80%91%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B49%E6%9C%8810%E6%97%A5%E9%A6%AC%E9%9B%B2%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%93%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD?mtc=30024</a>"},{"pid":"a711ec25373fab40d5288626484b6f58120980c0","tid":812841,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T03:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/112506_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https